1. Poslala je *poslu* u grad (She sent the job to the city).
2. Oni su na *poslu* cijelu noć (They were working all night).
3. Moram se pripremiti za *poslu* (I need to prepare for the job).
4. On je vrlo uspješan na *poslu* (He is very successful at work).
5. Ona je izgubila *poslu* (She lost her job).